title: Meta to wind down NFTs on platforms amid crypto bust
description:
Meta Platforms Inc is
cutting off support for digital collectibles or non-fungible
tokens  on its platforms less than a year after rolling it
out, as the crypto market continues to spiral.
           ... | March 13,  2023
